↑ Ashley D,Orenstein DM(2005).Sociological theory:Classical statements (6th ed.).Boston,MA,USA:Pearson Education,3-5,32-36
↑ Ashley D,Orenstein DM(2005).Sociological theory:Classical statements (6th ed.).Boston,MA,USA:Pearson Education,3-5,38-40
